## Pull Request Requirements

{% if use_commitizen %}
{% include 'template/_partials/conventional-commits.jinja' %}
{% endif %}
{% if use_precommit %}
- Pre-commit checks must pass
{% endif %}
- All tests must pass
- New features include tests
- Documentation is updated as needed
- PRs target the `main` branch
- All commits must be GPG-signed: `git config --global commit.gpgsign true`

## Code Review

All submissions require review. CODEOWNERS are automatically assigned as reviewers.

